                 Sincerely,

            </mj-text>
                <mj-text>
                    <strong>Sherie Cornish Gordon</strong>, Chief of Staff
                </mj-text>
                <mj-text>
                    <strong>Kristen Gould</strong>, Director of Marketing <br> <br>
Co-Leads, Polytechnic Implementation Communications Working Group

                </mj-text>
            </mj-column>
        </mj-section>
